# AI Agent Context Standards

## Standard Context Files

This project provides standard context files that AI coding assistants automatically discover:

### Root-Level Files

| File | Purpose | Discovered By |
|------|---------|---------------|
| `AGENTS.md` | Primary AI agent instructions (canonical source) | Claude Code, Cursor, Codex, OpenCode, Aider |
| `CLAUDE.md` | Claude-specific instructions and quick reference | Claude Code |
| `CODEX.md` | OpenAI Codex instructions | Codex |
| `ARCHITECTURE.md` | System architecture overview | All tools |
| `README.md` | Project overview | All tools |
| `CONTRIBUTING.md` | Contribution guidelines | All tools |

